{"tid":2437280,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到身邊嘅人終有一日會死就覺得好難過","createTime":"2021-03-07T18:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T08:47:17.000Z","uid":367597,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd9a1bc46ebcfe5d4a340fced74b22081ed9b92","tid":2437280,"uid":367597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:37:23.000Z","msg":"有時夜麻麻瞓唔著就會諗起呢樣嘢，生離死別永遠係人最控制唔到嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人會知道自己屋企人會唔會聽日就死，另一半會唔會突然有啲咩事，朋友會唔會不辭而別，父母終有一日會走，想像唔到佢哋走咗我會有幾傷心，冇咗佢哋嘅日子到底可以點捱落去，甚至去到撳焚化爐粒掣嗰下係有幾唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者係我早過佢哋走，佢哋同我身邊嘅人會有幾咁傷心，死咗之後我又會去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每過一日都係喺倒數緊自己同身邊所有人嘅死期，人終有一死，到底每一日做緊嘅嘢有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唉又諗到眼sipsip"},{"pid":"9557e3527c429640f1c3a809da8ac67d0d142c5d","tid":2437280,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"調返轉諗<br />\n人都會死<br />\n不如活在當下捉緊每個時機"},{"pid":"24063b5084a3ed111f0da4a068dad822bc48685b","tid":2437280,"uid":174174,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:39:33.000Z","msg":"假如你人生剩低一個月，列出十樣你會做嘅嘢"},{"pid":"8f82be448c859ee1451edf3c4b18ba52dc09133c","tid":2437280,"uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:39:47.000Z","msg":"以前都有咁諗 <br />\n<br />\n但你有冇見過 BB 仔果種 新生命力 ? <br />\n<br />\n舊人唔走<br />\n新人就冇得出世 <br />\n地球位置有限<br />\n有人走就有人入<br />\n人人平等 <br />\n大自然定律<br />\n<br />\n識咁諗之後舒服啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b7cb049d5eebdcfcc408b55813caa903214dff4","tid":2437280,"uid":310908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日諗諗下就會喊好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登睇到啲講屋企人過身嘅po都會喊到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e092e0af261ee1274b5bc456d4a4c3a6eff8cf","tid":2437280,"uid":367597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9557e3527c429640f1c3a809da8ac67d0d142c5d","tid":2437280,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"調返轉諗<br />\n人都會死<br />\n不如活在當下捉緊每個時機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"我諗法係死咗大家都係塵歸塵土歸土，李嘉誠同毒撚一樣最後所有人就咩都唔係，生前幾燦爛都冇用，冇嘢帶得落棺材，咁活在當下同我頹廢一生有咩分別"},{"pid":"8e46de9a5ef4ec170fc2d48846829b9e30e5d7ed","tid":2437280,"uid":367597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f82be448c859ee1451edf3c4b18ba52dc09133c","tid":2437280,"uid":61443,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:39:47.000Z","msg":"以前都有咁諗 <br />\n<br />\n但你有冇見過 BB 仔果種 新生命力 ? <br />\n<br />\n舊人唔走<br />\n新人就冇得出世 <br />\n地球位置有限<br />\n有人走就有人入<br />\n人人平等 <br />\n大自然定律<br />\n<br />\n識咁諗之後舒服啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:46:05.000Z","msg":"道理我都明，但接受唔到自己同身邊嘅人要經歷呢啲事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d6047a37c30cb3bbcb1a219f0361afdb089966","tid":2437280,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:46:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3570d853e13b8afbd75fef06762cd18be874541","tid":2437280,"uid":310908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:47:10.000Z","msg":"我18歲生日嘅凌晨就係喺到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為覺得離爸媽離開我又近左一年 <br />\n最近成日喺到諗 如果今日係我last day我會做啲乜野"},{"pid":"9376eff1032a14b51e81e452b5dbbdbe6d5967a9","tid":2437280,"uid":367597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b7cb049d5eebdcfcc408