ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T19:03:12.000Z","msg":"要當每一日都係最後一日咁去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為你根本就唔知自己幾時死唔知身邊人幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dee1efd65626be0713bca9bec8f662e7b1c3a8a","tid":2437280,"uid":145923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0e092e0af261ee1274b5bc456d4a4c3a6eff8cf","tid":2437280,"uid":367597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9557e3527c429640f1c3a809da8ac67d0d142c5d","tid":2437280,"uid":38904,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:38:32.000Z","msg":"調返轉諗<br />\n人都會死<br />\n不如活在當下捉緊每個時機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:44:46.000Z","msg":"我諗法係死咗大家都係塵歸塵土歸土，李嘉誠同毒撚一樣最後所有人就咩都唔係，生前幾燦爛都冇用，冇嘢帶得落棺材，咁活在當下同我頹廢一生有咩分別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T19:03:49.000Z","msg":"分別就係當下一刻是燦爛定on99"},{"pid":"ca807c26f59c9f8998446262bd3347293641f1de","tid":2437280,"uid":200344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbd775a775a7325b117557bb666779a9bfb3b3b","tid":2437280,"uid":357936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T18:54:53.000Z","msg":"我爸爸死了三十年了，放心，沒事的。日子還是要過，大家一起曾渡過的時光是死亡也不能磨滅的。<br />\n<br />\n我幾十年後也會死，老實說，我不怕，我希望身邊的人也不要懼怕我的死亡，尤其是我另一半。大家在這個世界上的相遇，對我而言，其實就是永恆。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T19:32:26.000Z","msg":"你好浪漫"},{"pid":"9dc65f286b491dd2d2ad42ab56b9e07dfd36ec2d","tid":2437280,"uid":382327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T20:51:44.000Z","msg":"前幾年老母走咗 走得好突然 而家諗起都係好想喊"},{"pid":"3757205a7ca23a66e3218b1091c48bd13600bbda","tid":2437280,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f38439c55a02498605bfdffc5b047ea6a658425","tid":2437280,"uid":28620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24063b5084a3ed111f0da4a068dad822bc48685b","tid":2437280,"uid":174174,"like":4,"dislike"